<node id="2011">
  <data key="d0">2011</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">2011 represents the baseline year of a recorded data series capturing metric values across prominent universities worldwide. Stanford University recorded the highest value at 94.3, followed by Princeton University at 94.2. University of California, Los Angeles registered 87.7, while University of Michigan recorded 83.4. Columbia University's value stood at 81.0, University of Hong Kong at 79.2, and University of Pennsylvania at 79.5. Northwestern University reported 75.9, University of Tokyo recorded 75.6, Georgia Institute of Technology measured 75.3, and University of California, Santa Barbara registered 75.0. National University of Singapore recorded 72.9, University of California, San Diego measured 73.2, New York University reported 63.9, and Karolinska Institute recorded the lowest value at 67.0. These measurements collectively establish 2011 as a foundational reference point for comparative institutional metrics across these leading academic institutions globally.&lt;SEP&gt;2011 represents a year with a recorded metric value of 58.3 for London School of Economics and Political Science.&lt;SEP&gt;2011 represents a year in which Australian National University recorded a metric value of 67.0.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2011 with an associated metric value of 70.7 for Peking University.&lt;SEP&gt;2011 represents a year with a recorded value of 65.0 for University of California, Davis.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2011 with a recorded value of 64.9 for Brown University.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b28e9a9e510f49ec3c13c959d79a75b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cff3e5960042c3ac2cd8086fa2cb0b8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aae47578acbeb722129493e1909c490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dff9f2843ac34903f1edcc91d064ec37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1000880d5bd07e21676a9676f48be75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e25f9ab35a9bf924916d78888cfd12f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71fc2bcc705632bb203b8138d9fe7c12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62667299648fbb5a1bc04726aefeaf2a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd9b9d225ae67c42bd9fac8f03af691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d202571e3a96b3bdbef19301c384031&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed705f3efcf0a3a0a4afbc320cf14fce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-861a75f78daeaa810908e3a989b80fdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-259c0e33cab48d182a66bd6c289ec01f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6590cd120d2bec87c7751f8ea9b56ed8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60be69e5f86095e634367cd1dea861a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8958d12aa92692c8fb3bfb766ad6e41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94ab4ec01d51d0734a362a17fdcac9d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8403b64c17da9b8d05e7153784bebd5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db7f39ecd543540106b3b66070aa4a5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-881f2a19041e8308add6dbef8f69309b</data>
