<node id="2012">
  <data key="d0">2012</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">2012 represents a single year for which metric values were recorded across multiple prestigious universities worldwide. Stanford University recorded the highest value at 93.9, followed by Princeton University at 92.9. Columbia University and University of California, Los Angeles both recorded values in the upper 80s range at 87.5 and 87.3 respectively. University of Pennsylvania recorded 84.9, while University of Michigan recorded 82.8. Northwestern University recorded 76.2, and Georgia Institute of Technology recorded 77.0.

Among additional institutions, University of Tokyo recorded 74.3, Karolinska Institute recorded 73.1, University of Hong Kong recorded 72.3, University of California, Santa Barbara recorded 72.1, and University of California, San Diego recorded 73.0. National University of Singapore recorded 70.9, while New York University recorded the lowest value at 69.0. These data points collectively represent a comparative snapshot of institutional metrics across leading academic institutions during 2012.&lt;SEP&gt;2012 represents a year with a recorded metric value of 66.0 for London School of Economics and Political Science.&lt;SEP&gt;2012 represents a year in which Australian National University recorded a metric value of 71.2.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2012 with an associated metric value of 65.6 for Peking University.&lt;SEP&gt;2012 represents a year with a recorded value of 71.2 for University of California, Davis.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2012 with a recorded value of 65.6 for Brown University.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b28e9a9e510f49ec3c13c959d79a75b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cff3e5960042c3ac2cd8086fa2cb0b8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aae47578acbeb722129493e1909c490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dff9f2843ac34903f1edcc91d064ec37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1000880d5bd07e21676a9676f48be75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e25f9ab35a9bf924916d78888cfd12f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71fc2bcc705632bb203b8138d9fe7c12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62667299648fbb5a1bc04726aefeaf2a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd9b9d225ae67c42bd9fac8f03af691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d202571e3a96b3bdbef19301c384031&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed705f3efcf0a3a0a4afbc320cf14fce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-861a75f78daeaa810908e3a989b80fdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-259c0e33cab48d182a66bd6c289ec01f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6590cd120d2bec87c7751f8ea9b56ed8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60be69e5f86095e634367cd1dea861a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8958d12aa92692c8fb3bfb766ad6e41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94ab4ec01d51d0734a362a17fdcac9d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8403b64c17da9b8d05e7153784bebd5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db7f39ecd543540106b3b66070aa4a5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-881f2a19041e8308add6dbef8f69309b</data>
