  <data key="d0">2015</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">2015 is a reference year for which metric values were recorded across multiple prominent universities worldwide. Stanford University recorded the highest value at 92.9, followed by Princeton University at 90.9. University of California, Los Angeles reported 85.5, while Columbia University recorded 84.4. University of Pennsylvania and University of Michigan reported values of 81.0 and 80.9 respectively. Northwestern University recorded 79.2, and University of Tokyo reported 76.1.

Additional institutions recorded the following metric values for 2015: Georgia Institute of Technology at 72.8, National University of Singapore at 73.3, New York University at 69.9, University of California, Santa Barbara at 70.0, University of California, San Diego at 68.6, and Karolinska Institute at 66.8. University of Hong Kong recorded the lowest value among all listed institutions at 67.5.&lt;SEP&gt;2015 represents a year with a recorded metric value of 70.9 for London School of Economics and Political Science.&lt;SEP&gt;2015 represents a year in which Australian National University recorded a metric value of 66.5.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2015 with an associated metric value of 65.2 for Peking University.&lt;SEP&gt;2015 represents a year with a recorded value of 63.7 for University of California, Davis.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2015 with a recorded value of 64.1 for Brown University.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b28e9a9e510f49ec3c13c959d79a75b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cff3e5960042c3ac2cd8086fa2cb0b8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aae47578acbeb722129493e1909c490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dff9f2843ac34903f1edcc91d064ec37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1000880d5bd07e21676a9676f48be75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e25f9ab35a9bf924916d78888cfd12f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71fc2bcc705632bb203b8138d9fe7c12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62667299648fbb5a1bc04726aefeaf2a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd9b9d225ae67c42bd9fac8f03af691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d202571e3a96b3bdbef19301c384031&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed705f3efcf0a3a0a4afbc320cf14fce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-861a75f78daeaa810908e3a989b80fdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-259c0e33cab48d182a66bd6c289ec01f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6590cd120d2bec87c7751f8ea9b56ed8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60be69e5f86095e634367cd1dea861a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8958d12aa92692c8fb3bfb766ad6e41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94ab4ec01d51d0734a362a17fdcac9d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8403b64c17da9b8d05e7153784bebd5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db7f39ecd543540106b3b66070aa4a5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-881f2a19041e8308add6dbef8f69309b</data>
