<node id="2016">
  <data key="d0">2016</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">2016 represents a year for which metric values were recorded across multiple prominent universities worldwide. Stanford University recorded the highest value at 93.9, marking the end of its data series, followed by Princeton University at 90.1. University of California, Los Angeles and Columbia University recorded 86.8 and 86.1 respectively, while University of Pennsylvania registered 85.2. University of Michigan recorded 82.4, and Northwestern University registered 79.5. National University of Singapore recorded 79.2, Karolinska Institute recorded 77.5, and New York University recorded 77.2. Georgia Institute of Technology and University of California, Santa Barbara both recorded 72.1 and 72.2 respectively, while University of California, San Diego recorded 72.2. University of Tokyo and University of Hong Kong recorded 71.1 and 71.0 respectively for the same year.&lt;SEP&gt;2016 represents a year with a recorded metric value of 81.3 for London School of Economics and Political Science.&lt;SEP&gt;2016 represents a year in which Australian National University recorded a metric value of 69.5.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2016 with an associated metric value of 72.0 for Peking University.&lt;SEP&gt;2016 represents a year with a recorded value of 71.0 for University of California, Davis.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2016 with a recorded value of 69.6 for Brown University.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b28e9a9e510f49ec3c13c959d79a75b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cff3e5960042c3ac2cd8086fa2cb0b8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aae47578acbeb722129493e1909c490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dff9f2843ac34903f1edcc91d064ec37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1000880d5bd07e21676a9676f48be75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e25f9ab35a9bf924916d78888cfd12f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71fc2bcc705632bb203b8138d9fe7c12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62667299648fbb5a1bc04726aefeaf2a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd9b9d225ae67c42bd9fac8f03af691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d202571e3a96b3bdbef19301c384031&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed705f3efcf0a3a0a4afbc320cf14fce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-861a75f78daeaa810908e3a989b80fdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-259c0e33cab48d182a66bd6c289ec01f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6590cd120d2bec87c7751f8ea9b56ed8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60be69e5f86095e634367cd1dea861a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8958d12aa92692c8fb3bfb766ad6e41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94ab4ec01d51d0734a362a17fdcac9d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8403b64c17da9b8d05e7153784bebd5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db7f39ecd543540106b3b66070aa4a5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-881f2a19041e8308add6dbef8f69309b</data>
